RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTMS_MARGIN_COMPONENT.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_COMPONENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_COMPONENT.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_COMPONENT.COMPONENT = LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.COMPONENT

LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.COMPONENT = LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_MARGIN_CCY.CCY = LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CCY

LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.COMPONENT = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.BRANCH_CODE = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_EFFDATE.CCY = LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CCY

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT B.CUSTOMER_NO, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORROWERS A, OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.CUSTOMER_NO UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'AL' FROM DUAL

SELECT DISTINCT A.MARGIN_COMPONENT, B.DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF_MARGIN A, LFTMS_MARGIN_DEFINITION B WHERE A.MARGIN_COMPONENT = B.MARGIN_COMPONENT AND A.MARGIN_BASIS = 'T' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE IN (SELECT REGEXP_SUBSTR(?,'[^#]+', 1, LEVEL) FROM DUAL CONNECT BY REGEXP_SUBSTR(?, '[^#]+', 1, LEVEL) IS NOT NULL)
SELECT DISTINCT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.BRANCH_CODE=LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.BRANCH_CODE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO=LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CUSTOMER_NO = LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.CUSTOMER_NO AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.COMPONENT = LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.COMPONENT AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE = LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.FROM_BASIS_AMT = LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.FROM_BASIS_AMT AND LFTMS_MARGIN_RATE.CCY = LFTMS_PARTICIPANT_MARGIN_RATE.CCY

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO PARTICIPANT, A.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTM_CUSTOMER a WHERE A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O'
